description:
"Inside the Machine" demo soundtrack by mA2E, demo ranked 1st at Deadline 2024 oldschool demo compo.
Still is from the demo by Steffest.

Watch the demo running here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pzFPVMruHFQ

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
title: Amiga music: mA2E - Inside the Machine demo OST (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
